	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Your program you put in the ROM isn't RAM.When the system boots up, it has garbage in it. Usually it's cleared on boot up, you have to store the variables you need in it at the spot you want them. Before your program starts, do a LDA #$NUMBER STA Label to put it there, there's no way around it, you have to.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


