	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you want something to be in RAM when your program starts, copy it from ROM to RAM in the init code. This is exactly how the cc65 runtime library handles .segment "DATA".

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


